derivedAttributes.attrExprVal:
CASE  WHEN UPPER(SRC_DIM_STORE.STORE_TYPE) ='RETAIL' AND UPPER(SRC_DIM_STORE.STORE_NAME) LIKE '%RTL-%' THEN REPLACE(SRC_DIM_STORE.STORE_NAME,'RTL-','') WHEN UPPER(SRC_DIM_STORE.STORE_COUNTRY_ABBR)='US' AND UPPER(SRC_DIM_STORE.STORE_NAME) IN ('JUSTFAB','FABKIDS','FABLETICS','SHOEDAZZLE') THEN SRC_DIM_STORE.STORE_NAME + ' ' + SRC_DIM_STORE.STORE_COUNTRY_ABBR
ELSE SRC_DIM_STORE.STORE_NAME
END

sqlParams.paramVal: select 'ID' CONFIG_KEY, MASTER_CONFIG_ID CONFIG_VALUE from etl_audit.DIY_MASTER_CONFIG where upper(project) = upper('$$ProjectName') and upper(job_flow) = upper('$$JobFlowName')
SELECT 'rpt_from_key' param_key, date_key param_val FROM mart.dim_date WHERE full_date =to_timestamp_ntz('$FS_config_val.RPT_MNTH_LW')

INSERT INTO $DO_TDWH_SN_EDW_MART_AGG_SALES_EUR_HOURLY ( DATETIME_KEY,DATE_KEY,HOUR_KEY,REPORT_VERSION,STORE_KEY,ORDER_CLASSIFICATION_KEY,ORDER_DETAIL_KEY,ORDER_CHANNEL_KEY,ORDER_STATUS_KEY,ORDER_CNT,ORDER_UNITS,ORDER_REDEEMED_MEMBERSHIP_CREDIT_CNT,ORDER_REDEEMED_REFUND_CREDIT_CNT,ORDER_REDEEMED_GIFT_CARD_CREDIT_CNT,ORDER_REDEEMED_OTHER_CREDIT_CNT,CASH_TRANSACTION_CNT,BILLED_FIRST_ATTEMPT_CNT,CASH_COLLECTED_CNT,PAYMENT_AMT,TAX_AMT,ORDER_TRANSACTION_CASH_COLLECTED_AMT,REFUNDED_CASH_CNT,REFUNDED_STORE_CREDIT_CNT,CHARGEBACK_CNT,ORDER_SUBTOTAL_AMT,ORDER_DISCOUNT_AMT,ORDER_SHIPPING_REVENUE_AMT,ORDER_COGS_AMT,ORDER_COST_PRODUCT_AMT,ORDER_COST_PRODUCT_MARKDOWN_AMT,ORDER_COST_SHIPPING_AMT,ORDER_COST_OUTBOUND_FREIGHT_AMT,ORDER_COST_SHIPPING_SUPPLIES_AMT,ORDER_REDEEMED_MEMBERSHIP_CREDIT_AMT,ORDER_REDEEMED_REFUND_CREDIT_AMT,ORDER_REDEEMED_GIFT_CARD_CREDIT_AMT,ORDER_REDEEMED_OTHER_CREDIT_AMT,REFUNDED_CASH_AMT,REFUNDED_STORE_CREDIT_AMT,CHARGEBACK_AMT,CHARGEBACK_TAX_AMT,OTHER_CASH_CREDIT_ISSUED_AMT,REFUND_CASH_CREDIT_ISSUED_AMT,SERVICE_REVENUE_AMT,SAME_MONTH_CREDIT_REDEEMED_AMT,RETURN_CNT,RETURN_ITEM_CNT,RETURN_COST_PRODUCT_AMT,RETURN_COST_PRODUCT_MARKDOWN_ADJUSTMENT_AMT,RETURN_COST_SHIPPING_AMT,DIM_CURRENCY_EXHANGE_KEY,META_CREATE_DATETIME,META_UPDATE_DATETIME,META_CREATE_JOB_EXEC_ID,META_UPDATE_JOB_EXEC_ID) 
WITH SRC_DIM_STORE  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_DIM_STORE.STORE_KEY AS STORE_KEY
	,SRC_DIM_STORE.REGION_ABBR AS REGION_ABBR
 FROM 
	$DO_TDWH_SN_EDW_MART_DIM_STORE SRC_DIM_STORE  
 WHERE 
	SRC_DIM_STORE.STORE_GROUP_ID NOT BETWEEN 1 AND 8 
) 
,SRC_dim_currency_exchange  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_dim_currency_exchange.CURRENCY_EXCHANGE_KEY AS CURRENCY_EXCHANGE_KEY
 FROM 
	$DO_TDWH_SN_EDW_MART_DIM_CURRENCY_EXCHANGE SRC_dim_currency_exchange  
 WHERE 
	upper(SRC_dim_currency_exchange.currency_exchange_conversion_type)= 'EUR' 
) 
,  jnr_sales_dataset_eur 
AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_SALES_DATASET.DATETIME_KEY AS DATETIME_KEY
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.DATE_KEY AS DATE_KEY
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.HOUR_KEY AS HOUR_KEY
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.REPORT_VERSION AS REPORT_VERSION
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.STORE_KEY AS STORE_KEY
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_CLASSIFICATION_KEY AS ORDER_CLASSIFICATION_KEY
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_DETAIL_KEY AS ORDER_DETAIL_KEY
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_CHANNEL_KEY AS ORDER_CHANNEL_KEY
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_STATUS_KEY AS ORDER_STATUS_KEY
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_CNT AS ORDER_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_UNITS AS ORDER_UNITS
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_REDEEMED_MEMBERSHIP_CREDIT_CNT AS ORDER_REDEEMED_MEMBERSHIP_CREDIT_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_REDEEMED_REFUND_CREDIT_CNT AS ORDER_REDEEMED_REFUND_CREDIT_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_REDEEMED_GIFT_CARD_CREDIT_CNT AS ORDER_REDEEMED_GIFT_CARD_CREDIT_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_REDEEMED_OTHER_CREDIT_CNT AS ORDER_REDEEMED_OTHER_CREDIT_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.CASH_TRANSACTION_CNT AS CASH_TRANSACTION_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.BILLED_FIRST_ATTEMPT_CNT AS BILLED_FIRST_ATTEMPT_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.CASH_COLLECTED_CNT AS CASH_COLLECTED_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.PAYMENT_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR ,1)  AS payment_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.TAX_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1)
 AS tax_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_TRANSACTION_CASH_COLLECTED_AMT * COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR ,1)
 AS order_transaction_cash_collected_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.REFUNDED_CASH_CNT AS REFUNDED_CASH_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.REFUNDED_STORE_CREDIT_CNT AS REFUNDED_STORE_CREDIT_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.CHARGEBACK_CNT AS CHARGEBACK_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_SUBTOTAL_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1)
 AS order_subtotal_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_DISCOUNT_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1)
 AS order_discount_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_SHIPPING_REVENUE_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS order_shipping_revenue_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_COGS_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS order_cogs_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_COST_PRODUCT_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS order_cost_product_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_COST_PRODUCT_MARKDOWN_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS order_cost_product_markdown_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_COST_SHIPPING_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS order_cost_shipping_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_COST_OUTBOUND_FREIGHT_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS order_cost_outbound_freight_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_COST_SHIPPING_SUPPLIES_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS order_cost_shipping_supplies_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_REDEEMED_MEMBERSHIP_CREDIT_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS order_redeemed_membership_credit_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_REDEEMED_REFUND_CREDIT_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS order_redeemed_refund_credit_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_REDEEMED_GIFT_CARD_CREDIT_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS order_redeemed_gift_card_credit_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_REDEEMED_OTHER_CREDIT_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS order_redeemed_other_credit_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.REFUNDED_CASH_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS refunded_cash_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.REFUNDED_STORE_CREDIT_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS refunded_store_credit_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.CHARGEBACK_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS chargeback_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.CHARGEBACK_TAX_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS chargeback_tax_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.OTHER_CASH_CREDIT_ISSUED_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS other_cash_credit_issued_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.REFUND_CASH_CREDIT_ISSUED_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS refund_cash_credit_issued_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.SERVICE_REVENUE_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS service_revenue_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.SAME_MONTH_CREDIT_REDEEMED_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS same_month_credit_redeemed_amt
	,SRC_dim_currency_exchange.CURRENCY_EXCHANGE_KEY AS CURRENCY_EXCHANGE_KEY
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.RETURN_COST_PRODUCT_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS return_cost_product_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.RETURN_CNT AS RETURN_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.RETURN_ITEM_CNT AS RETURN_ITEM_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.RETURN_COST_PRODUCT_MARKDOWN_ADJUSTMENT_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS return_cost_product_markdown_adjustment_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.RETURN_COST_SHIPPING_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS return_cost_shipping_amt
	,$MP_meta_datetime  AS meta_datatime
	,$$AuditId  AS meta_job_exec_id
  FROM 
	$DO_TDWH_SN_EDW_MART_AGG_SALES_HOURLY SRC_SALES_DATASET 

 INNER JOIN
 SRC_DIM_STORE 
ON
(SRC_SALES_DATASET.STORE_KEY =SRC_DIM_STORE.STORE_KEY ) 

 INNER JOIN
 SRC_dim_currency_exchange 
ON
(1=1) 
WHERE 	UPPER(SRC_DIM_STORE.REGION_ABBR) = 'EU' AND SRC_SALES_DATASET.DATE_KEY >= $MP_rpt_from_key 
)

WITH SRC_DIM_STORE  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_DIM_STORE.STORE_KEY AS STORE_KEY
	,SRC_DIM_STORE.REGION_ABBR AS REGION_ABBR
 FROM 
	$DO_TDWH_SN_EDW_MART_DIM_STORE SRC_DIM_STORE  
 WHERE 
	SRC_DIM_STORE.STORE_GROUP_ID NOT BETWEEN 1 AND 8 
) 
,SRC_dim_currency_exchange  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_dim_currency_exchange.CURRENCY_EXCHANGE_KEY AS CURRENCY_EXCHANGE_KEY
 FROM 
	$DO_TDWH_SN_EDW_MART_DIM_CURRENCY_EXCHANGE SRC_dim_currency_exchange  
 WHERE 
	upper(SRC_dim_currency_exchange.currency_exchange_conversion_type)= 'EUR' 
) 
,  jnr_sales_dataset_eur 
AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_SALES_DATASET.DATETIME_KEY AS DATETIME_KEY
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.DATE_KEY AS DATE_KEY
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.HOUR_KEY AS HOUR_KEY
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.REPORT_VERSION AS REPORT_VERSION
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.STORE_KEY AS STORE_KEY
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_CLASSIFICATION_KEY AS ORDER_CLASSIFICATION_KEY

	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_UNITS AS ORDER_UNITS
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_REDEEMED_MEMBERSHIP_CREDIT_CNT AS ORDER_REDEEMED_MEMBERSHIP_CREDIT_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_REDEEMED_REFUND_CREDIT_CNT AS ORDER_REDEEMED_REFUND_CREDIT_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_REDEEMED_GIFT_CARD_CREDIT_CNT AS ORDER_REDEEMED_GIFT_CARD_CREDIT_CNT

	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.PAYMENT_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR ,1)  AS payment_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.TAX_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1)
 AS tax_amt

 AS order_transaction_cash_collected_amt

 AS order_discount_amt

	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_COST_SHIPPING_SUPPLIES_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS order_cost_shipping_supplies_amt

	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.ORDER_REDEEMED_OTHER_CREDIT_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS order_redeemed_other_credit_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.REFUNDED_CASH_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS refunded_cash_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.REFUNDED_STORE_CREDIT_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS refunded_store_credit_amt

	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.CHARGEBACK_TAX_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS chargeback_tax_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.OTHER_CASH_CREDIT_ISSUED_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS other_cash_credit_issued_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.REFUND_CASH_CREDIT_ISSUED_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS refund_cash_credit_issued_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.SERVICE_REVENUE_AMT*COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS service_revenue_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.SAME_MONTH_CREDIT_REDEEMED_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS same_month_credit_redeemed_amt
	,SRC_dim_currency_exchange.CURRENCY_EXCHANGE_KEY AS CURRENCY_EXCHANGE_KEY
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.RETURN_COST_PRODUCT_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS return_cost_product_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.RETURN_CNT AS RETURN_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.RETURN_ITEM_CNT AS RETURN_ITEM_CNT
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.RETURN_COST_PRODUCT_MARKDOWN_ADJUSTMENT_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS return_cost_product_markdown_adjustment_amt
	,SRC_SALES_DATASET.RETURN_COST_SHIPPING_AMT *COALESCE(SRC_SALES_DATASET.CONVERSION_RATE_EUR,1) AS return_cost_shipping_amt
	,$MP_meta_datetime  AS meta_datatime
	,$$AuditId  AS meta_job_exec_id
  FROM 
	$DO_TDWH_SN_EDW_MART_AGG_SALES_HOURLY SRC_SALES_DATASET 

 INNER JOIN
 SRC_DIM_STORE 
ON
(SRC_SALES_DATASET.STORE_KEY =SRC_DIM_STORE.STORE_KEY ) 

 INNER JOIN
 SRC_dim_currency_exchange 
ON
(1=1) 
WHERE 	UPPER(SRC_DIM_STORE.REGION_ABBR) = 'EU' AND SRC_SALES_DATASET.DATE_KEY >= $MP_rpt_from_key 
)
